  "title": "Commodity Specialist / procurement - Medical Device MNC/ East #HMS",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage a commodity group specific to a manufacturing plant or region. </li><li>Initiate and follow through cost reduction programs including total cost bench-marking, identify opportunities and execution.</li><li>Carry out periodic price and contract review / negotiations with suppliers. </li><li>Actively manage work flow in SAP and ensure that all price agreements are appropriately loaded.</li><li>Supplier Management activities which include New Supplier On-boarding, Supplier Agreement or T&C Checklist, Supplier Periodic Business Reviews, Scorecards and Audits.</li></ul><p>up to 7.5k<br />Kaki bukit<br /></p><p>Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p><p></p><p></p>",
